<section>
  <p>
    Hello, this is Amin. For the past 2 years I’ve been leading Design Ops at Accurat, a data visualization, design, and development studio based in Milan and New York. Prior to Accurat I lived in Berlin and worked for Mozilla. First as a design system designer and later as the sole designer for experimental browsers such as Firefox for <span class="small-caps">TV</span>s and smart displays. In 2010 I started my design career opening a one-man studio that I run for 6 years.
